---
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout
    title="PBIS"
    description="Green Schools Foundation proudly sponsors the district's PBIS (Positive Behavior Intervention and Support) initiative, promoting positive behavior and academic success for all students."
    showBreadcrumbs={true}
    breadcrumbs={[
        { name: "Foundation Initiatives", href: "/foundation-initiatives" },
        { name: "PBIS", href: "/pbis" }
    ]}
>
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Positive Behavior Intervention and Support</h2>
        <p>
            Green Schools Foundation is proud to be a funding sponsor for the Green Local School District's PBIS initiative. PBIS (Positive Behavior Intervention and Support) is a nationally recognized, evidence-based framework that helps schools create positive learning environments where all students can succeed.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 mb-6">
            This tiered system of support allows staff to create and teach expectations that help all students feel successful. Through the PBIS program, behavior expectations are taught proactively, and positive behaviors are consistently acknowledged and reinforced.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <img src="/images/pbis-award-2025.webp" alt="PBIS 2025 District Award for Green Local Schools" class="w-full h-72 object-contain rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-gray-100" />
            <img src="/images/pbis.webp" alt="PBIS Program at Green Local Schools" class="w-full h-72 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg" />
            <img src="/images/pbis-neighborhood-grants.webp" alt="Neighborhood Grants supporting Green Local Schools" class="w-full h-72 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PBIS in Action at Green Elementary -->
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>PBIS in Action</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
                <img src="/images/pbis-cross-collaboration.webp" alt="Cross collaboration between 5th and 2nd grade classes" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-4" />
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cross Collaboration at Green Elementary School</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Mrs. Clark's fifth-grade class earned their BulldogStrong pom reward and chose to celebrate by visiting Mrs. Kuwatch's second-grade class! Students had fun sharing books with their younger peers â€” a great way to build community and provide peer mentorship.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <img src="/images/pbis-dumping-poms.webp" alt="Students dumping PBIS poms into school-wide bin" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-4" />
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Dumping "poms" at Green Elementary</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Ms. Shumaker's cross-categorical class at Green Elementary was delighted to dump their PBIS-earned poms into the school-wide bin, eager to gain extra recess.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-6 text-center">Green Local Schools PBIS Expectations</h2>
        <div class="grid-3">
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.166 4.999A11.954 11.954 0 0010 1.944 11.954 11.954 0 0017.834 5c.11.65.166 1.32.166 2.001 0 5.225-3.34 9.67-8 11.317C5.34 16.67 2 12.225 2 7c0-.682.057-1.35.166-2.001zm11.541 3.708a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">Be Safe</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                    Making choices that keep yourself and others safe in all school environments.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">Be Kind</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                    Treating others with respect, empathy, and compassion every day.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent-600 mb-2">Be Responsible</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                    Taking ownership of your actions and making good decisions.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>What is PBIS?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            PBIS is a proactive approach to establishing the behavioral supports and social culture needed for all students to achieve social, emotional, and academic success. Rather than waiting for problems to occur, PBIS focuses on prevention and teaching positive behaviors.
        </p>

        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Key Components</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Clear Expectations</span>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Defined behavioral expectations that are taught and reinforced</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Positive Reinforcement</span>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Recognition and rewards for demonstrating expected behaviors</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Consistent Response</span>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Uniform approach to addressing behavioral concerns</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Data-Driven Decisions</span>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Using information to identify and address student needs</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">The Three Tiers</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-700">Tier 1: Universal Support</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">School-wide expectations and supports for all students (~80% of students)</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-700">Tier 2: Targeted Support</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Additional interventions for students who need more support (~15% of students)</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-700">Tier 3: Intensive Support</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Individualized interventions for students with significant needs (~5% of students)</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Benefits of PBIS</h2>
        <div class="grid-3">
            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Academic Success</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Students spend more time learning when behavioral disruptions are reduced.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3zM6 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM16 18v-3a5.972 5.972 0 00-.75-2.906A3.005 3.005 0 0119 15v3h-3zM4.75 12.094A5.973 5.973 0 004 15v3H1v-3a3 3 0 013.75-2.906z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Positive Climate</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Creates a welcoming school environment where students feel safe and respected.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Social-Emotional Growth</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Students develop important life skills like self-regulation and empathy.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Research-Based Results</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
            PBIS is nationally recognized as an essential building block to academic success for all students. Schools implementing PBIS with fidelity have reported:
        </p>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Decreased disciplinary referrals</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Improved school climate</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Increased instructional time</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Higher academic achievement</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Better student-teacher relationships</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Reduced suspensions and expulsions</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>GSF's Role in PBIS</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Green Schools Foundation provides funding support for the district's PBIS initiative, helping to ensure that all students in Green Local Schools have access to this proven approach to creating positive learning environments.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2V6h10a2 2 0 00-2-2H4zm2 6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H8a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4zm6 4a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Financial Support</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Our funding helps cover the costs of PBIS training, materials, recognition systems, and other resources needed to implement this program effectively across all Green Local Schools.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section text-center">
        <h2>Learn More About PBIS</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            For more information about the PBIS program in Green Local Schools or how you can support this initiative, please contact us.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=PBIS Program Inquiry" class="button-primary mr-4">
            Contact Us
        </a>
        <a href="/foundation-initiatives" class="button-secondary">
            View All Initiatives
        </a>
    </div>
</ContentLayout>
